<br>
This joyous event was turned sour by the wanton murder of a young *unarmed* gnomish mage by the Paladins.  This young mage had dared to stand off to the side to watch the proceedings (unarming himself in the presence of the King) and was summarily executed.  This is not the same King Tearis Thex whom I have fought for all these many years!  The King Thex that I know would never kill an unarmed gnome.<br>
<br>
Does this mean that King Tearis Thex is under the influence of some evil force?  Laugh if you must, but the King of Ak'Anon is also no more -- he has been replaced by a clockwork, operated by an evil &quot;mini-me.&quot;  Has now the King of Felwithe been replaced by an evil imposter?  Only time will tell, but I, for one, will sleep a little less soundly.<br>
<br>
Serius, Formerly Enchanter to King Tearis Thex<br>
<br>
/ooc Of course, the real explanation is that our beloved guides and GM get their jollies by killing players -- what fun ! <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub6.ezboard.com/fluclin71335roleplaying.showMessage?topicID=47.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub6.ezboard.com/fluclin71335roleplaying.showMessage?topicID=63.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br></td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub6.ezboard.com/fluclin71335roleplaying.emailToFriend?topicID=65.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub6.ezboard.com/fluclin71335roleplaying.threadControl?topicID=65.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/deleteThreadFire.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub6.ezboard.com/fluclin71335roleplaying.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=65.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub6.ezboard.com/fluclin71335roleplaying.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=65.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub6.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="luclin71335general">General<option value="luclin71335trading">Trading<option value="luclin71335frm7">Spell Trading<option value="luclin71335dragonsandtheplanes">Dragons and the Planes<option value="luclin71335frm23">GMT Gamers<option value="luclin71335frm8">Scars of Velious<option value="luclin71335roleplaying">Roleplaying<option value="lucli